column.name: SQL_DATA_ACCESS
column.StoredType: enum('CONTAINS SQL', 'NO SQL', 'READS SQL DATA', 'MODIFIES SQL DATA')|0e

column.name: LOG_TYPE
column.Comment: The log type to which the transactions were written.

column.name: TRANSACTION_COUNTER
column.Comment: Number of transactions written to the log

column.name: COMPRESSED_BYTES_COUNTER
column.Comment: The total number of bytes compressed.

column.name: UNCOMPRESSED_BYTES_COUNTER
column.Comment: The total number of bytes uncompressed.

column.name: COMPRESSION_PERCENTAGE
column.Comment: The compression ratio as a percentage.

column.name: FIRST_TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP
column.Comment: When the first transaction was written.

column.name: LAST_TRANSACTION_TIMESTAMP
column.Comment: When the last transaction was written.

column.name: START_LSN
column.Comment: LSN of the first block in the file.

column.name: END_LSN
column.Comment: LSN after the last block in the file.

column.name: IS_FULL
column.Comment: 1 iff file has no free space inside.

column.name: CONSUMER_LEVEL
column.Comment: All redo log consumers registered on smaller levels than this value, have already consumed this file.

column.name: PRIVILEGE_CHECKS_USER
column.Comment: User name for the security context of the applier.

column.name: REQUIRE_ROW_FORMAT
column.Comment: Indicates whether the channel shall only accept row based events.

column.name: REQUIRE_TABLE_PRIMARY_KEY_CHECK
column.Comment: Indicates what is the channel policy regarding tables without primary keys on create and alter table queries

column.name: ASSIGN_GTIDS_TO_ANONYMOUS_TRANSACTIONS_TYPE
column.Comment: Indicates whether the channel will generate a new GTID for anonymous transactions. OFF means that anonymous transactions will remain anonymous. LOCAL means that anonymous transactions will be assigned a newly generated GTID based on server_uuid. UUID indicates that anonymous transactions will be assigned a newly generated GTID based on Assign_gtids_to_anonymous_transactions_value

column.name: ASSIGN_GTIDS_TO_ANONYMOUS_TRANSACTIONS_VALUE
column.Comment: Indicates the UUID used while generating GTIDs for anonymous transactions

column.name: CHANNEL_NAME
column.Comment: The replication channel name that connects source and replica.

column.name: HOST
column.Comment: The source hostname that the replica will attempt to switch over the replication connection to in case of a failure.

column.name: PORT
column.Comment: The source port that the replica will attempt to switch over the replication connection to in case of a failure.

column.name: NETWORK_NAMESPACE
column.Comment: The source network namespace that the replica will attempt to switch over the replication connection to in case of a failure. If its value is empty, connections use the default (global) namespace.

column.name: WEIGHT
column.Comment: The order in which the replica shall try to switch the connection over to when there are failures. Weight can be set to a number between 1 and 100, where 100 is the highest weight and 1 the lowest.

column.name: MANAGED_NAME
column.Comment: The name of the group which this server belongs to.

column.name: CHANNEL_NAME
column.Comment: The replication channel name that connects source and replica.

column.name: MANAGED_NAME
column.Comment: The name of the source which needs to be managed.

column.name: CONFIGURATION
column.Comment: The data to help manage group. For Managed_type = GroupReplication, Configuration value should contain {"Primary_weight": 80, "Secondary_weight": 60}, so that it assigns weight=80 to PRIMARY of the group, and weight=60 for rest of the members in mysql.replication_asynchronous_connection_failover table.

column.name: HEARTBEAT_INTERVAL
column.Comment: Number of seconds after which a heartbeat will be sent .

column.name: COMPRESSION_ALGORITHM
column.Comment: Compression algorithm used for data transfer between master and slave.

column.name: ZSTD_COMPRESSION_LEVEL
column.Comment: Compression level associated with zstd compression algorithm.

column.name: GTID_ONLY
column.Comment: Indicates if this channel only uses GTIDs and does not persist positions.

column.name: LAST_HEARTBEAT_TIMESTAMP
column.Comment: Shows when the most recent heartbeat signal was received.

column.name: puserid
column.Comment: 发布该好乡镇宣传的用户标识

column.name: pfile_list
column.Comment: 上传的图片等资源文件名称列表

column.name: pbegindate
column.Comment: 开始宣传日期，默认提交日期

column.name: pid
column.Comment: 对应的好乡镇宣传标识

column.name: support_state
column.Comment: 状态，0：待接受；1：已接受；2：拒绝；3：取消

column.name: sfile_list
column.Comment: 上传的介绍图片等文件名称列表

column.name: userlvl
column.Comment: 用户级别，默认普通用户，可扩展设计对应业务功能
